lyrics:
[verse 1]
In the city streets of Southside, a story unfolds
A crazy family with struggles, battling against the cold
Frank Gallagher and his crew, shamelessly wild
Their dysfunctional lives, always leaving us beguiled

[chorus]
Oh, Shameless, oh Shameless, a series so insane
With laughter and tears, it drives us all insane
Oh, Shameless, oh Shameless, a rollercoaster ride
We're hooked on the chaos, we can never hide
